<TITLE>Tools</TITLE>
</HEAD><BODY BGCOLOR="#EEFFFF">
<B><A HREF="/">Home</A> | <A HREF="/">Up</A> | <A HREF="/web/help/">Help</A> | <A HREF="/web/scripts/comment.acgi">Send a comment</A></B>
<HR>
<IMG SRC="/web/images/pstaricn.gif" align="left"><H1>General Tools</H1>
if you want access to the University of Michigan Hospital computer system, see the <A HREF="/web/UMpsych/resource/index.htm">UM Resource Page</A>.<P>
Here are useful references from the Web:<BR clear=all>
<H3>Web searching facilities</H3>
<UL>
<LI><A HREF="http://www.infoseek.com">Infoseek</A> (very sophisticated)
<LI><A HREF="http://www.lycos.com/">Lycos</A> server (very comprehensive)
<LI> <A HREF="http://www.altavista.digital.com">Alta vista</A> (fast)
<LI>the <A HREF="http://www.cs.colorado.edu/home/mcbryan/WWWW.html">World Wide Web Worm</A> (WWWW)
</UL>
<H3>Subject-based Web Indicies</H3>
<UL>
<LI>the <A HREF="http://www.yahoo.com/">Yahoo</A> pages
<LI>the <A HREF="http://www.einet.net/galaxy.html">EINet Galaxy</A>
<LI>the <A HREF="http://www.w3.org/hypertext/DataSources/bySubject/Overview.html">WWW Virtual Library</A> maintained by the W3 consortium.
</UL>
<H3>Other useful resources</H3>
<ul>
 <LI><A HREF="gopher://ashpool.micro.umn.edu:70/00/Weather/Michigan/Detroit">local weather</A> forecast (Detroit)
 <LI>Time magazine's <A HREF="http://www.pathfinder.com/@@NK*7ygAAAAAAwIrQ/time/daily/time/1995/latest.html">Daily News</A> site
 <LI>gopher site that finds<A HREF="gopher://cwis.rice.edu:1103/7areacode"> 
telephone area codes</A> for you
\t<li>an online <a href="gopher://odie.niaid.nih.gov/77/.thesaurus/index">thesaurus</a>
\t<li>an online <a HREF="http://crnvmc.cern.ch/FIND/DICTIONARY?">dictionary</a>
 <LI>an online <A HREF="http://wombat.doc.ic.ac.uk/">dictionary of computer terms</A>
<LI><A HREF="http://www.ncsa.uiuc.edu/SDG/Software/Mosaic/NCSAMosaicHome.html">Starting Points</A>
</UL>
<H3>Software</H3>
<UL>
 <LI>gopher connection to the <A HREF="gopher://gopher.archive.merit.edu:70/11/.software-archives">University of Michigan Software Archives</A>
<LI>a listing of helpful <a href="/web/help/macware.htm">software for using the Web</a> is available from our HELP page.
</ul>
