<IMG ALIGN="left" VSPACE=5 HSPACE=3 SRC="/web/images/psychlogo.gif"><H2>The University of Michigan Department of Psychiatry Home Page</H2>
<BR clear=all>
<UL>
<LI><A HREF="brochure/"><B>Information about the University of Michigan Department of Psychiatry</B></A>
<LI>Department <A HREF="announce/"><B>News and Events</B></A>: includes
the <A HREF="/web/UMpsych/announce/grandrnd/index.htm">Grand Rounds Schedule</A> and other information of interest to the department
<LI>The <A HREF="resource/"><B>UM Resource page</B></A>: including links to UM computers such as Medline, Mirlyn, Pathnet, etc. and the <A HREF="/web/UMpsych/resource/directry.htm">Department e-mail directory</A>
</UL>
<P>

Links to other World Wide Web pages:
<UL>
<LI>General <A HREF="/web/psychRef/"><B>References in Psychiatry</B></A>
<LI>General <A HREF="/web/medRef/"><B>References in Medicine</B></A>
<LI><A HREF="/web/tools/"><B>General tools</B></A> available on the WWW (search tools, news, weather, etc.)
<LI>For those new to the World Wide Web, there is an <A HREF="/web/help/newuser.htm">introduction page</A>.  We are in the process of generating more <A HREF="/web/help/">help files</A>.
</UL>
<P>
You can also go to the <A HREF="http://www.med.umich.edu/">University of Michigan Hospital Home Page</A> or the <A HREF="http://www.umich.edu/">University of Michigan Home Page</A> from here.
