<BODY bgcolor=#FFFFFF text=#000000 link="#CC0000" alink="#FF3300">
<H1>The AACAP homepage has moved to their new server in Washington D.C.
Please change your bookmark to <A HREF="http://www.aacap.org/web/aacap/">http://www.aacap.org/web/aacap/</A></H1>
<P><HR><H1>
<IMG ALIGN=left SRC="/web/aacap/aacapkid.gif"  hspace=5>
<A HREF="/web/aacap/award.htm" ><IMG ALIGN=right  SRC="/web/images/award/awards.gif"hspace=5 border=0></A>

<P><HR><H1>
The American Academy of Child  & Adolescent Psychiatry Homepage
</H1>
<IMG vspace=4 SRC= "/web/images/dot_clear.gif">
<BR clear=all>
 
<hr >
<UL>
<LI><A HREF="brochure.htm">Introduction </A>to the American Academy of Child & Adolescent Psychiatry
<LI><A HREF="/web/aacap/whatsnew.htm">What's new</A>
<LI><A HREF="factsFam/"><B>Facts for Families</B></A> our award-winning series of 51 fact sheets written to help children and their families is available in English, <A HREF="/web/aacap/apntsFam/index.htm">Spanish</A> and <A HREF="/web/aacap/infofami/index.htm">French</A>.
<LI><A HREF="rptcard.htm">Research Report Card</A>, research plan on Child and Adolescent Mental Disorders in USA.
<LI><A HREF="/web/aacap/govafair/legalert.htm">the AACAP Legislative Alerts</A> from the AACAP Department of Government Affairs.
<LI><A HREF="/web/aacap/meeting/index.htm">Upcoming Meetings and Events</A> including the<A HREF="meeting/"> Annual Meeting of the AACAP</A> with the <A HREF="/web/aacap/meeting/papers.htm">Call for papers</A>.
<LI><A HREF="http://www.psych.med.umich.edu/web/psychRef/">Mental Health WWW Resources</A>
<LI><A HREF="pubs.htm"> Publications Catalog </A> 
<LI><A HREF="contact.htm">Directory</A>
</UL>






<HR>
<center><H2>American Academy of Child & Adolescent Psychiatry</H2>
<B>3615 Wisconsin Avenue, NW<BR>
Washington,DC 20016-3007</B><P>
<IMG vspace=2 SRC= "/web/images/dot_clear.gif"> <BR>
tel. <B> 1-202-966-7300</B><BR>
fax  <B>1-202-966-2891</B><P>
URL  <B>http://www.psych.med.umich.edu/web/aacap/</B></center><P>
<IMG hspace=10 SRC= "/web/images/dot_clear.gif"> <BR>

These pages have been designed to keep you informed of current AACAP events, as well as offer access to various AACAP literature.  
If this is your first time on the World Wide Web, place your mouse <A HREF="http://www.psych.med.umich.edu/web/help/newuser.htm">in this area</A> and click once.<P>


<B><font size=+1> <A HREF="brochure.htm">Introduction </A>to the American Academy of Child & Adolescent Psychiatry</B></font size=+1>
with <A HREF="/web/aacap/brochure.htm#What we are doing">what we are  doing </A> and <A HREF="/web/aacap/brochure.htm#Who we are ">who we are </A>and a<A HREF="/web/aacap/presidentword.htm"> word from the President</A>. </P>


<h2>The AACAP on the Internet</h2>
