<TITLE>PSI homepage</TITLE>
</HEAD><BODY BGCOLOR="#EEFFFF">
<IMG ALIGN="left" SRC="psilogo.gif" vspace=10 hspace=10><IMG vspace=8 SRC="/web/images/dot_clear.gif"><H1>Psychiatric Society <br>for Informatics</H1>
<BR clear=all>
<P>

<center><B>Welcome</B> to the Homepage of the Psychiatric Society for Informatics.  <P><B>The purpose of the PSI is to promote the understanding and <BR>use of informatics and information technology in Psychiatry.</B></center>
<hr>
<UL>
<LI><A HREF="history.htm"><B>History</B></A>
<P>
<LI><B>Current Organization</B>
<DD><A HREF="comemb.htm"><B>Steering Committee</B></A>
<DD>Annual Meeting Committee: under formation.  If interested, contact <A HREF="mailto:nalessi@umich.edu">Norm Alessi</A> or <A HREF="mailto:mhuang@umich.edu">Milton Huang</A>
<DD><B>Publishing Committee</B>
<DD><A HREF="bylaws.htm"><B>Bylaws</B></A>
<P>
<LI><B>Current News</B>
<DD>We had our first meeting in New York in May.
 A <A HREF= "/web/psi/mtg/psisum96.htm">summary</A> is available.<P>

<DD><A HREF="/web/psi/mtg/indexRTC.htm"> <B>1997 Next Meeting</A> in San Diego, May 17, 1997</B><P>
<LI><A HREF="/web/psi/newsletter/index.htm"><B>PSI Newsletter</B></A>
<LI><A HREF="/web/psi/listserv/index.htm"><B>PSI Listserv</B></A>
<LI><A HREF="appform.htm"><B>Membership Information and Application Form</A></B>
</UL>
<HR>

The PSI logo was created by <A HREF="/web/UMpsych/staff/mhuang/">Milton Huang</A> and is copyright by him.  This website is supported by the University of Michigan Department of Psychiatry.

