<IMG SRC="/web/images/pstaricn.gif" align="left"><IMG vspace=7 SRC= "/web/images/dot_clear.gif"> <BR><H1>What is Psychiatry Star?</H1><BR CLEAR=ALL><IMG vspace=4 SRC= "/web/images/dot_clear.gif"> <BR>

 <H4>| <B>Current</B> | 
<A HREF="/web/pStar/indexprev.htm"><B>Previous </B></A>  |</H4>



Psychiatry Star is the Web site run through the <A HREF="/web/UMpsych/infmatic/">Psychiatric Informatics</A> Program of the University of Michigan Department of Psychiatry.  The Psychiatry Star Team is guided by the Program Director, <A HREF="/web/UMpsych/staff/nalessi/">Norman Alessi, MD</A>.  The people that make the magic are:
<DL>
<DD><IMG SRC="/web/images/purpstar.gif"><A HREF="/web/UMpsych/staff/mhuang/">Milton Huang, MD</A>, Assistant Director of Psychiatric Informatics and Lecturer in Psychiatry
<DD><IMG SRC="/web/images/purpstar.gif"><A HREF="/web/UMpsych/staff/osteo/">
Paul Quinlan MD,</A> Informatics Fellow 
<DD><IMG SRC="/web/images/purpstar.gif"><A HREF="/web/UMpsych/staff/ddifranc/">Duane Di Franco, MD </A>, Psychiatry Resident
<DD><IMG SRC="/web/images/purpstar.gif"><A HREF="http://www-personal.umich.edu/~evanfeib">Evan Feibusch MD </A> Psychiatry Resident
<DD><IMG SRC="/web/images/purpstar.gif"><A HREF="/web/UMpsych/staff/rosaHP/rosa.htm
">Rosalie Jung Ging MD,</A> Psychiatrist
<DD><IMG SRC="/web/images/purpstar.gif"><A HREF="http://www-personal.umich.edu/~
afarkas">Adam Farkas,</A> 4th year Medical Student 

<DD><IMG SRC="/web/images/purpstar.gif"><A HREF="http://www-personal.umich.edu/~
ssachdev">Ravi Sachev,</A> UM Computer Engineering undergraduate student.
