<H1> UM Resources </H1>
<H3>Telnet Links to other computer systems</H3>
Your computer will allow you to jump directly to a telnet link if you have NCSA telnet version 2.6 installed.  You can directly <A HREF="gopher://gopher.archive.umich.edu:7055/40/mac/util/comm/ncsatelnet2.6.sit.hqx">download</A> this program from the Mac Archives gopher.
<UL>
<LI><A HREF="telnet://um-medline.merit.edu">Medline</A> connection for literature searches.  Your user name should be "UMI," followed by your social security number without dashes.
<LI><A HREF="http://muscat.gdb.org/repos/medl/">WWW Medline,</A> a new link, without using telnet connection.

<LI><A HREF="telnet://mirlyn.telnet.lib.umich.edu:23/">Mirlyn</A> connection to find references in the University of Michigan Libraries.  There is also a page of information on <A HREF="http://www.lib.umich.edu/libhome/mirlyn/mirlynpage.html">how to use MIRLYN</A>.
<LI>Connect to the <A HREF="telnet://vaum.med.umich.edu:2001">VANET</A> if you have a password for the VA computer system.
<LI><A HREF="telnet://pathnet.med.umich.edu">Pathnet</A> connection to get pathology and radiology results
<LI><A HREF="telnet://login.itd.umich.edu">login server</A> to the ITD system
<LI><A HREF="telnet://umce.itd.umich.edu">UM computing environment</A> server where you can find information about you computer account.
<LI>The <A HREF="telnet://confer.itd.umich.edu">Confer</A> II conference computer where medical students communicate about medical school on the mednet confer.  Enter "confer mednet" when you get the prompt "confer%"
<LI><A HREF="telnet://hermes.merit.edu">Merit</A> connection (Which Host? prompt)
</UL>
<H3>Web Links to UM Resources</H3>
<UL>

<LI> <A HREF="directry.htm">E-mail, Psychiatry Department Directory  </A>
<LI><A HREF="http://web500gw.itd.umich.edu:8888/Mo%3dUniversity%20of%20Michigan,%20c%3dUS">X.500 address book</A> for looking up anyone in the University of Michigan
<LI>list of all UM <A HREF="http://www.med.umich.edu/oca/changes.htm">pager numbers</A>.
<LI><A HREF="http://toucan.hosp.med.umich.edu/physlook.html"> Physician Data Search</A>


 

<LI><A HREF ="http://www.lib.umich.edu/libhome/Taubman.lib/tml.homepage.html">Taubman 
medical library homepage</A>
<LI><A HREF="http://www.lib.umich.edu/libhome/Taubman.lib/lib.illarticle.html">UM
Interlibrary loan request form</A>

</UL>

<H3>Gopher Links to other computer systems</H3>
<UL>
<LI><A HREF="gopher://gopher.archive.merit.edu:7055/11/mac">Mac Archives</A> gopher from Merit: a place to download Mac shareware and freeware
<LI>UM <A HREF="gopher://gopher.itd.umich.edu/11/">GOpher BLUE</A>: the gopher resource of the University of Michigan including computer sales and the X.500 address book
</UL>

