<HEAD>
<TITLE>UM Psychiatry News and Events</TITLE>
</HEAD><BODY BGCOLOR="EEEEEE">
<B> <IMG hspace=3 SRC= "/web/images/dot_clear.gif"><A HREF="/">Home</A> | <A HREF="/">Up</A> | <A HREF="/web/tools/">Tools</A> | <A HREF="/web/help/">Help</A> | <A HREF="/web/scripts/comment.acgi">Send a comment</A></B><HR>
<IMG ALIGN="left" vspace=5 SRC="/web/images/psychlogo.gif"><H2> University of Michigan Psychiatry News and Events</H2>
<BR CLEAR=ALL><P>
<B>Events</B></A></B><UL>
<LI><A HREF="/web/UMpsych/announce/grandrnd/index.htm">Psychiatric Grand Rounds.</A>
Weekly Meetings are held on Wednesdays 10:30-12:00 am.  Guest Speakers who have made significant contributions in their field alternate with Resident Case presentations.
<P>
<LI><A HREF="/web/UMpsych/announce/seminar.htm"> Consultation Liaison Seminars.</A> Seminars cover
basic topics encountered in consultation work, presented by program faculty at the beginning of
each rotation. For the remainder of the rotation, faculty and residents participate together in a
weekly consultation/psychosomatic medicine journal club.
<P>
<LI><A HREF="/web/UMpsych/infmatic/lecture/index.htm">Informatic Lectures.</A> This lecture series covers a broad range of topics in Medical Informatics and the use of Information technology, including library information systems, database management, medical decision making, telecommunication, and multimedia applications.  It is designed for the entire University of Michigan community.
<P>
<LI><A HREF="evolbiolcurrent.htm">Evolutionary Biology Series</A>. 
A Colloquium on Evolution and Human Behavior, sponsored by UM Institute for Social Research and Human Behavior Program and organized by Randolph Nesse and Richard Nisbett.<A HREF="/web/UMpsych/announce/evolbiolcurrent.htm"> Current</A>
<P>

<LI><A HREF="neurobiol.htm">Neuroscience Lecture Series.</A> Neurobiology of 
Cocaine Abuse.Organized by Karley Y. Little M.D.
<P>
</UL>
<B>News from the University Department of Psychiatry</B>
<UL>
<BR>
<LI><IMG SRC="/web/images/new.gif">John Greden MD was elected Chairman of the Board of Directors of the Faculty Group Practice.
<LI><IMG SRC="/web/images/new.gif">Michelle Riba, M.D., will be Associate Chair of Education and Academic Affairs and Michael 
<LI><IMG SRC="/web/images/new.gif">Michael Jibson, M.D., Ph.D., will be Director of Resident and Fellow Education. 



<LI>Robert Zucker PH.D was elected President-elect: Division of Addiciton in American Psycholgy Association.
<LI>Huda Akil PhD. was elected President elect of the the ACNP.


<LI>Lynne Lyons M.D. was elected Secretary of the Michigan Psychiatric Society's Resident Section.  She is also the GRASS MITS representative to the APA
<LI>Anita Kumar-Gill M.D. was elected as a Representative to the House Officers' Association, repressesnting psychiatry's interests.
<LI><A HREF="/web/UMpsych/announce/seminar.htm">David Knesper MD</A> was nominated as Teacher of the Year, the second year in a row.
<LI> Effective June 1, 1996, Sheila Marcus, M.D., will become director of a newly constituted Adult Ambulatory Division
<LI>
<A HREF="/web/UMpsych/brochure/consult.htm">Thomas Carli M.D.</A>
 will become director of Managed Psychiatric Services and the Michigan Center for Diagnosis and Referral (CDR).
<LI> Rajiv Tandon, M.D., was appointed Director of the new Adult Hospital Division,

<LI><A HREF="/web/UMpsych/staff/nalessi/">
<B>Norman Alessi MD</B></A>has been appointed Deputy Editor, Electronic Journal American Journal for<TD> Psychiatry, 1996-1999


<LI><A HREF="/web/UMpsych/brochure/about.htm"><B>Michelle Riba MD</B></A>has been elected for Trustee at Large for the American Psychiatric Association.
<A HREF="/web/UMpsych/brochure/consult.htm">
<LI><B>Thomas Carli MD</B></A> was recently chosen as president-elect of the 1,100 member Michigan Psychiatric Society (the District Branch of the American Psychiatric Association). .
<LI><B>Rachel Glick MD</B> Director, Medical Student Education, is Recipient of the APA's CA Roeske MD Certificate of Recognition for Excellence in Medical Student Education
<LI><B>Cheryl King, Ph.D.,</B> was recently elected president-elect of the American Association of Suicidology
<P>
<LI><A HREF="/web/UMpsych/announce/MHcode.htm"><B>New Mental Health Code</B></A>

<A HREF="/web/UMpsych/announce/matchL.htm"><B>Match List</B></A>
<P>
<LI><B>Awards</B>
