<HEAD>
<TITLE>Psychiatry Grand Rounds</TITLE>
</HEAD>
<BODY BGCOLOR="EEEEEE">
<B> <IMG hspace=3 SRC= "/web/images/dot_clear.gif"><A HREF="/">Home</A> | <A HREF="./">Up</A> | <A HREF="/web/tools/">Tools</A> | <A HREF="/web/help/">Help</A> | <A HREF="/web/scripts/comment.acgi">Send a comment</A></B>
<HR>
<IMG SRC="http://www.psych.med.umich.edu/web/umpsych/psycicon.gif"
" ALIGN="left" vspace=15 ><H1>Department of Psychiatry<BR>Current Grand Rounds </H1>
<CENTER><B>Wednesdays - 10:30 AM - 12:00 Noon</B><BR>
<B>MCHC (Maternal & Child Auditorium) </B><P>

