<P><H5>
The University of Michigan Medical School is accredited by the Accreditation Council for Continuing Medical Education to sponsor continuing medical education for physicians.  The University of Michigan Medical School designates this continuing medical education activity for 1.5 credit hours in Category 1 of the Physician's Recognition Award of the American Medical Association.</H5><BR>

