http://www.psych.med.umich.edu:80/web/aacap/rptcard.htm 141.214.71.83 19970121043307 text/html 60501
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
MIME-Version: 1.0
Server: WebSTAR/1.2.4 ID/39
Message-ID: <af09be67.151338@141.214.71.83>
Date: Tuesday, 21-Jan-97 04:29:27 GMT
