<center><H1>The American Academy of Child & Adolescent Psychiatry Directory</H1></center>

<center>
<B>3615 Wisconsin Avenue, NW<BR>
Washington, DC 20016-3007</B><P>

tel. <B> 1-202-966-7300</B><BR>
fax  <B> 1-202-966-2891</B><P>
URL  <B>http://www.psych.med.umich.edu/web/aacap/</B><P></center>








The American Academy of Child and Adolescent Psychiatry is not equipped to respond to
inquiries via E-mail at this time.  For information inquiries or <A HREF="/web/aacap/wherehlp.htm">physician referrals</A>, please include a
mailing address in your correspondence to AACAP 3615 Wisconsin Avenue, N.W., Washington,
D.C. 20016.<p>
A <A HREF="/web/aacap/maillist.htm">Mailing List</A> is available for sale when certain criteria have been met.

