<HR><P>
<H1>The PSI Listserv</H1>
<P>
We now have a <B>Listserv</B> based at Indiana thanks to the work of Marvin Miller.
 This mailing list allows rapid communications through email to the selection of 
members who have joined. This service is available only to members.  
<P>
In order to be put on the list, contact the Secretary-Treasurer,
Milton Huang, <A HREF= "mailto:mhuang@umich.edu">mhuang@umich.edu</A> I keep the membership list and the database of address and email information.  We encourage all members to join!
<P>
Once added to the list, you should get automated notices about <A HREF="howwork.htm">
how mailing lists work </A>and <A HREF= "expect.htm">expectations of appropriate use</A>.
<P>
Once you understand the details of automated mailing lists, you might want to look at the <A HREF="commands.htm">reference card</A> which summarizes the instructions you can issue.
<P>
Let us know if there are other useful documents regarding listserv use that we should link to this page.<!--FOOT-->
