<HEAD>
<TITLE>Medications</TITLE>
</HEAD><BODY BGCOLOR="#EEFFFF">
<B><A HREF="/">Home</A> | <A HREF="./">Up</A> | <A HREF="/web/tools/">Tools</A> | <A HREF="/web/help/">Help</A> | <A HREF="/web/scripts/comment.acgi">Send a comment</A></B>
<HR>
<IMG SRC="/web/images/pstaricn.gif" align="left"><H1>Medications</H1>
<UL>
<LI>the NIMH <A HREF="gopher://gopher.nimh.nih.gov:70/00/documents/nimh/other/Medicate">patient information pamphlet on medications</A> for mental illness
<LI>The <A HREF="http://uhs.bsd.uchicago.edu/~bhsiung/tips/tips.html">Psychopharmcology Tips page</A>, maintained by <A HREF="http://uhs.bsd.uchicago.edu/~bhsiung/tips.htmlbhsiung/dr.bob.html">Dr. Robert Hsiung</A>.  This page summarizes tips on medication management that have been posted to the psycho-pharm discussion group run by <A HREF="/web/intpsych/">InterPsych</A>.
<LI>Information about <A HREF="http://uhs.bsd.uchicago.edu/~bhsiung/augment.html">antidepressant augmentation</A>, created by <A HREF="http://uhs.bsd.uchicago.edu/~bhsiung/dr.bob.html">Dr. Robert Hsiung</A>.
<LI>The <A HREF="http://pharminfo.com/drugdb/db_mnu.html">Drug Database</A> from <A HREF="http://pharminfo.com/">PharmInfoNet</A>, sponsored by <A HREF="http://pharminfo.com/pialtd/piahp2.html">Pharmaceutical Information Associates</A>.  Alphabetically organized by trade name, this index lists drug indications and links to reviews from PIA's <A HREF="http://pharminfo.com/pubs/msb/msbmnu.html">Medical Sciences Bulletin</A> (MSB)
<UL><LI>You can also directly review the <A HREF="http://pharminfo.com/pubs/msb/msbmnu.html#msb_psycho">MSB articles on psychopharacologic drugs</A></UL>
<LI><A HREF="www.mentalhealth.com/p30.html">Psychiatric medications</A>from Mental HealthInternet 

</UL>
<H3>Password Protected Databases</H3>
<UL>
<LI><A HREF="http://www.icsi.net/GenRx.html">Physicians' GenRx</A>, published by Mosby: requires paid subscription

</UL>
