<IMG SRC="/web/images/pstaricn.gif" align="left" vspace=5><H1>Psychiatric and Psychological Institutions</H1><BR CLEAR=ALL>
<HR>
<H2><A NAME="societies">Societies</A></H2>
<UL>
<LI><A HREF="http://apa.org/">American Psychiatric Association</A>
<LI>the <A HREF="/web/psi/">Psychiatric Society for Informatics</A>
<LI>the homepage of the <A HREF="/web/aacap/"><FONT size=+1><B>American Academy of Child and Adolescent Psychiatry</B></FONT></A>: contains information about the AACAP as well as their <A HREF="/web/aacap/factsFam/">Facts for Families</A> series of pamphlets.
<LI>Milton's <A HREF="/web/intpsych/"><FONT size=+1><B>InterPsych</B></FONT></A> page: a description of the Interpsych organization and some of the services they provide, including email and IRC discussion forums
<LI><A HREF="http://www.sob.org/"> Society of Biological Psychiatry</A>
<LI><A HREF="http://www.shef.ac.uk/uni/projects/gpp/ ">GlobalPsych</A>: a confederation of co-operating individuals and organizations designed to promote cordial and wide ranging debate and investigation of issues in health, behavior, cognition and education, from a broad multi-disciplinary perspective. 
<LI>APsa: <A HREF="http://apsa.org/">The American Psychoanalytic Association</A>
<LI>the homepage of the <A HREF="http://www.lafayette.edu/allanr/scip.html">Society for Computers in Psychology</A>: a non-profit organization of researchers interested in applications of computers in psychology
<LI>The <A HREF="http://psych.hanover.edu/APS/">American Psychological Society</A>
<LI>PsychNET: the home of the <A HREF="http://www.apa.org/">American Psychological Association</A>
<LI>the Abraham A. Brill Library's <A HREF="http://www.interport.net/nypsan/">Freudnet</A>: contains information about the library and psychoanalysis
<LI><A HREF="http://www.umdnj.edu/~pulierml/AAP.home.html">Administrators in Academic Psychiatry</A>, a professional organization for the
education and networking of administrators of academic departments of
psychiatry
<LI>Los Angeles Institute and 
Society for Psychoanalytic Studies(LAISPS)<A HREF=" http://home.earthlink.net/~laisps/">LAISPS</A>
</A>

</UL>

<HR>
<H2><A NAME="Universities">Universities</A></H2>
<UL>
<LI><a href="/web/UMpsych/"><B><FONT size=+1>The University of Michigan Department of Psychiatry</FONT></B></a>
<LI>The <A HREF="http://cpmcnet.columbia.edu/dept/pi/">New York State Psychiatric Institute</A> Home Page
<LI>The <A HREF="http://www.med.nyu.edu/Psych/NYUPsych.Homepage.html">NYU Department of Psychiatry</A> homepage
<LI>The <A HREF="http://www.swmed.edu/home_pages/psych/Index.html">University of Texas Southwestern Medical Center</A> at Dallas Psychiatry Home Page
<LI>The Department of Psychiatry at <A HREF="http://neuroscience.ucdavis.edu/psychiatry/">UC Davis</A>
<LI><A HREF="http://www.brown.edu/Departments/Psychiatry/">Brown University</A> Department of Psychiatry and Human Behavior
<LI>The Psychiatry Project from the <A HREF="http://unixg.ubc.ca:780/~psychiat/ubcp_home.html">University of British Columbia</A>
<LI>The Center for Mental Health Policy and Services Research at the <A HREF="http://www.med.upenn.edu/~cmhpsr/">University of Pennsylvania Medical Center</A>
<LI><A HREF="http://www.pitt.edu/~wplib/">The University of Pittsburg</A> Department of Psychiatry
<LI>the <A HREF="http://w3socpsy.med.rug.nl/">The University of Groningen</A> Department of Social Psychiatry Homepage
<LI>the <A HREF="http://psych-9121.mgh.harvard.edu/">The Massachusetts General Hospital</A> Psychiatry Department homepage maintained by the MGH OCD Clinic: includes a list of their faculty and some of their publications
<LI>the <A HREF="http://http.bsd.uchicago.edu/~psychiatry/home.html">The University of Chicago</A> Department of Psychiatry
<LI>the <A HREF="http://www.iop.bpmf.ac.uk/">The Institute of Psychiatry</A> of London University
<LI>the <A HREF="http://psy.utmb.edu/"> The University of Texas Medical Branch Psychiatry Department</A> which contains information about their clinical programs, faculty, and more.
<LI><A HREF="http://www.phypc.med.wayne.edu/psyn/home.htm" NAME=">Wayne State</A> Department of Psychiatry & Behavioral Sciences
<LI><A HREF="http://www.mcl.tulane.edu/tmcinfo/psych_neuro/psnra01.htm">Tulane University</A> Department of Psychiatry and Neurology
<LI><A HREF="http://wpic.library.pitt.edu">The University of Pittsburgh</A>
<LI><A HREF="http://www.usask.ca/psychiatry/">The University of Saskatchewan,Psychiatry Department</A>
<LI><A HREF=" http://blizzard.cc.mcgill.ca/Psychiatry/TPRR.html">  Division of 
               Social & Transcultural Psychiatry</A> Department of Psychiatry
  McGill University, Montreal, Quebec.
<LI><A HREF="http://www.mcw.edu/psych/"> the Medical College of Wisconsin,</A>
<LI><A HREF="http://www.nemc.org/psych/depthome.htm">Tufts U Dept.Psychiatry</A>
<LI><A HREF="http://info.med.yale.edu/chldstdy/tsocd.htm"> Yale Child Study </A>



</UL>

<HR>
<H2><A NAME="research">Research Institutes</A></H2>
