<TITLE>Norman Alessi's CV</TITLE>
</HEAD><BODY BGCOLOR="EEEEEE">
<B> <IMG hspace=3 SRC= "/web/images/dot_clear.gif"><A HREF="/">Home</A> | <A HREF="/web/UMpsych/">Up</A> | <A HREF="/web/tools/">Tools</A> | <A HREF="/web/help/">Help</A> | <A HREF="/web/scripts/comment.acgi">Send a comment</A></B>
<HR>
<H1>CURRICULUM VITAE</H1><IMG SRC="alessi.gif"
ALT="Image of Dr. Norman Alessi" ALIGN=left HSPACE=10><br>
<font size=+2><font size=+3>N</font>orman Emil Alessi</font><br>
Department of Child and Adolescent Psychiatry<BR>
<a href="http://www.med.umich.edu">University of Michigan Medical Center</a><BR>
Ann Arbor, Michigan 48109<BR>
<A HREF="mailto:norman.alessi@med.umich.edu">norman.alessi@med.umich.edu</A><BR>
<br CLEAR=left>
<hr size=4>

<H2><center>Areas of Interest</center></H1>

<H3>Child and Adolescent Psychiatry</H3>
<ul>
<li><H4>Child and Adolescent Mood Disorders</H4>
<ol>
<li>	Phenomenology and nosology of affective disorders
		in children and adolescents
<li>	Comorbidity of affective disorders with other
		psychiatric disturbances
<li>	Treatment issues including treatment resistant
		depression in children and adolescents & the use
		of augmentation strategies
</ol>

<li><H4>Psychopharmacology</H4>
<ol>

<li>	The use of serotonin agonists and reuptake inhibitors in the treatment of childhood psychiatric disorders
<li>	The use of serotonin agonists in the treatment of aggression and rage in children and adolescents
</ol>
</ul>

<H3><center>Information Technology</center></H3>
<ul>
<li><H4>Multimedia</H4>
<ol>
<li>	Development of digitized information that can be transferred to a CD ROM fomat
<li>	Use of multimedia in education, research and clinical care of psychiatric patients
</ol>

<li><H4>Telemedicine</H4>
<ol>
<li>	Implementation of telemedicine in psychiatry
<li>	Development of clinical research protocols in the investigation of requirements for the implementation of 			telemedicine in psychiatry
<li>	Exploration of organizational and psychological barriers in the implementation of telemedicine
</ol>

<li><H4>Telecommunications</H4>
<ol>
<li>	Utilization of multimedia information in World Wide Web Homepage applications
<li>	Development of commercial applications of psychiatric care utilizing Internet
</ol>

<li><H4>Digitized Library of Psychopathology</H4>
<ol>
<li>	Investigation of the development of standardized digital video representations of psychiatric disorders
<li>	Integration of digital representations of psychiatric disorders in clinical care, research, etc.
</ol>

<li><H4>Medical Information Services (MIS)</H4>
<ol>
<li>	Development of expertise in the areas of MIS in psychiatry
<li>	The role of physicians in the development of MIS in large enterprise systems
</ol>

<li><H4>Psychiatric Informatics</H4>
<ol>
<li>	Development of a curriculum for teaching psychiatric informatics to general residents
<li>	Development of a psychiatric informatics fellowship
<li>	Development of a national society of psychiatric informatics
</ol>
</ul>

<hr size=4>

<H3><center>Bibliography</center></H3>
<ul>
<li>  <a href="pubs.htm">Completed Publications in Scientific
Journals</a>
<li>  <a href="books.htm">Books</a>
<li>  <a href="abstract.htm">Abstracts</a>
<li>  <a href="present.htm">Presentations, Posters, and Panel Discussions</a>
<li>  <a href="avprod.htm">Audio/Visual Productions</a>
</ul>

