<H3>Congratulations!</H3> 
 You just activated what is known as a hypertext link and jumped to a new Web Page.  Click on this link to <A HREF="newuser.htm">go back</A> to the previous page.  You may note that the hypertext link on this page is a different color from the one previous.  That is because your viewing program (or Web browser) keeps track of which pages you have seen and which ones you haven't.  If you <A HREF="newuser.htm">go back</A> now, you will see the link to this page will have changed since you have already seen this page and probably don't want to come back.



