<HEAD>
<TITLE>Informatics Didactics</TITLE>
</HEAD><BODY BGCOLOR="EEEEEE">
<B> <IMG hspace=3 SRC= "/web/images/dot_clear.gif"><A HREF="/">Home</A> | <A HREF="/web/UMpsych/infmatic/">Up</A> | <A HREF="/web/tools/">Tools</A> | <A HREF="/web/help/">Help</A> | <A HREF="/web/scripts/comment.acgi">Send a comment</A></B>
<HR>
<H1>UM Informatics Lecture Series</H1> 
In order to encourage academic interest and communication in the field of informatics, the Psychiatric Informatics program has organized the following lecture series.  Starting with the new year, meetings are scheduled from 5:00-6:30 in Mott Auditorium (F1540).  Go down the elevators to the first floor, turn left then it will be immediately on the right.<P>

We also support a page describing <font size=+2><A HREF="/web/UMpsych/infmatic/lecture/indexnews.htm">Informatics News and Events</A> </font>.<P>
 
There is also an electronic mailing list to keep updated on information and lecture changes.  Contact <A HREF="mailto:mhuang@umich.edu">&lt;mhuang@umich.edu&gt;</A> if you want to get on.

<TABLE ID="1" BORDER>
<TR><TD><B>Date<BR>Location</B>
<TD><B>Topic</B>
<TD><B>Description</B>
