<DOCHDR>
http://www.psych.med.umich.edu:80/web/aacap/govafair/terms.htm 141.214.71.83 19970121055338 text/html 15011
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
MIME-Version: 1.0
Server: WebSTAR/1.2.4 ID/39
Message-ID: <af09d150.151654@141.214.71.83>
Date: Tuesday, 21-Jan-97 05:50:08 GMT
