<H3>Did you:</H3>

<LI> access World Wide Web information<P>

<LI> call Senators/Representative <p>

<LI> send a fax to Senators/Representative<p>

<LI> send a letter to Senators/Representative <p>

<LI> visit the office of Senators/Represesentative called<p>

<LI> do something else not listed above.  Please describe:<br>
|<p>

<B><H3>Name of the Senators or representative</H3></B>
|<BR>
|<BR>
|<P>

<B>Which issues did you discuss</B>, what were your impressions of the legislator's position,	and is there any specific follow-up needed ?<br>
|<br>
|<br>
|<br>
|<br>
|<br>
|<p>


Was the information provided by the AACAP Department of Government Affairs helpful?
Suggestions/Comments:<br>
|<br>
|<br>
|<br>
|<br>
|<p>

<b>Thank you for these important contacts.</b>
<HR>


</HTML>
</DOC>
