         &gt;
      </TD></TR>
   <TR>
      <TD>
         <P>File Transfer Protocol (FTP)
      </TD><TD>
         <P>i This protocol uses a client/server model where users
         (clients) can connect to a document (file) serving computer,
         obtain a list of the different files available, then either
         copy one of these files from the server to their own
         computer or conversely load a file onto the server.
      </TD><TD>
         <P>Psycoloquy back issues:
