      </TD></TR>
   <TR>
      <TD>
         <P>Usenet news (also netnews)
      </TD><TD>
         <P>This protocol defines "newsgroups," each with a
         particular topic. A user signs on to a particular group and
         recieves copies of all the latest messages posted to the
         group. They can read messages or send messages back to the
         group.
      </TD><TD>
         <P>Psycoloquy back issues:
         &lt;news:sci.psychology.journals.psycoloquy&gt;</P>
         
