<HEAD>
<TITLE>Informatics Didactics</TITLE>
</HEAD><H2><A HREF="/">Home</A> | <A HREF="./">Up</A> | <A HREF="/web/tools/">Tools</A> | <A HREF="/web/help/">Help</A> | <A HREF="/web/scripts/comment.acgi">Send a comment</A></H2>
<HR>
<IMG SRC="dictlogo.gif" ALIGN=CENTER VSPACE=10><H1>Didactics</H1>
Educating others in the field of medical informatics and the use of information technologies is an important part of our projects.  This education occurs at the level of teaching Psychiatry residents, teaching Psychiatric Informatics fellows, and general instructional projects for the staff at the University of Michigan Hospitals both inside and outside of the Department of Psychiatry.<P>

In order to encourage academic interest and communication in the field of informatics, we have organized the <A HREF="/web/UMpsych/infmatic/lecture/"><B>UM informatics lecture series</B></A>.  Meetings are scheduled from 5:30-6:30 in room 1H203 in the main hospital.

<P>
Back to the <A HREF="/web/UMpsych/infmatic/">Informatics Homepage</A>
