<IMG SRC="mmlogo.gif" ALIGN=CENTER VSPACE=10>
<H1>Multimedia</H1>
 We are engaged in creating the Digital Library of Psychopathology (DLOPP), as well as studying the different ramifications of such a library including the creation of video standards, forming educational materials,  legal and ethical implications.
