<HEAD>
<TITLE>Informatics and Networks/Communication</TITLE>
</HEAD><H2><A HREF="/">Home</A> | <A HREF="./">Up</A> | <A HREF="/web/tools/">Tools</A> | <A HREF="/web/help/">Help</A> | <A HREF="/web/scripts/comment.acgi">Send a comment</A></H2>
<HR>
<IMG SRC="netlogo.gif" ALIGN=CENTER VSPACE=10>
<H1>Networks and Communication</H1>
 We are involved in exploring and expanding how psychiatric information can be safely communicated across local computer networks as well as networks, such as the Internet.  This includes efforts in designing and setting up World Wide Web serving for the <A HREF="/web/UMpsych/brochure/about.htm">UM Department of Psychiatry</A> and the <A HREF="/web/aacap/">American Academy of Child and Adolescent Psychiatry</A>.
<HR>
Back to the <A HREF="/web/UMpsych/infmatic/">Informatics Homepage</A>
