<li>Alessi, N.E. and Leventhal, B.  The Business of Academic Child and Adolescent Psychiatry.  A Workshop.  American Academy of Child and Adolescent Psychiatry, 1989.

<li>Alessi, N.E.:  The Psychological Consequences of Child Abuse:  Theoretical and Clinical Considerations.  Symposium.  American Academy of Child and Adolescent Psychiatry, 1989.

<li>Alessi, N.E.:  Language Disturbances in Child Psychiatric Populations.  Symposium.  American Academy of Child and Adolescent Psychiatry, 1989.

<li>Alessi, N.E.:  The Frequency and Severity of Speech and Language Disturbance in Child Psychiatric Inpatients.  American Academy of Child and Adolescent Psychiatry, 1989.

<li>Alessi, N.E.:  Stress-Induced Analgesia and Its Relationship to Child Abuse.  American Academy of Child and Adolescent Psychiatry, 1989.

<li>Alessi, N.E., and Eisner, S.J.:  The Characterization of Childhood Aggression Using the Overt Aggression Scale (OAS).  Society for Research in Child and Adolescent Psychopathology, 1990.

<li>Alessi, N.E., Eisner, S.J., and Knight, C.D.: The Association of Language Disturbances with Cognitive and Motoric Impairments in Psychiatrically Hospitalized Children.  Society for Research in Child and Adolescent Psychopathology, 1990.

<li>Alessi, N.E., and Eisner, S.J.:  Language Disturbances Significantly Association with Cognitive and Motoric Impairments in Psychiatrically Hospitalized Children.  Society of Biological Psychiatry, 1990.

<li>Alessi, N.E., Knight, C., Bergs, J., and Eisner, S.:  The Effects of Imipramine on TRH-induced Urinary Urgency.  American Academy of Child and Adolescent Psychiatry, Chicago, October, 1990.

<li>Alessi, N.E. and Shain, B.:  The Macintosh Computer:  Applications in the Pursuit of Academic Productivity.  American Academy of Child and Adolescent Psychiatry, Chicago, October, 1990.

<li>Alessi, N.E., Hunt, R., Garfinkel, B.:  Beyond Diagnostic Diffusion and Therapeutic Nihilism:  Medication Selection in the Difficult Case.  American Academy of Child and Adolescent Psychiatry, Chicago, October, 1990.

<li>Alessi, N.E. and Naylor, M.:  Research in Inpatient Child and Adolescent Units.  American Academy of Child and Adolescent Psychiatry, Chicago, October, 1990.

<li>Bos, T. and Alessi, N.E.:  An Open Clinical Trial of MAOI in Children with Major Depressive Disorder.  American Academy of Child and Adolescent Psychiatry, Chicago, October, 1990.

<li>Naylor, M.W., Alessi, N.E., Shain, B.M., King, C., and Shipley, J.E.:  Polysomnographic Sleep in Depressed Children and Adolescents.  American Academy of Child and Adolescent Psychiatry, Chicago, October, 1990.

<li>Zubieta, J. and Alessi, N.E.:  Trazodone in the Treatment of Childhood Disturbance?  Society of Biological Psychiatry, New Orleans, Louisiana, 1991.

<li>Alessi, N.E., Hunt, R., Gafney, G., and Steingard, R.:  The Computer is More than a Word Processor.  American Academy of Child and Adolescent Psychiatry, San Francisco, October, 1991.

<li>Livingston, R., Alessi, N., and Lenore, T:  Post-traumatic Stress in Children.  American Academy of Child and Adolescent Psychiatry, San Francisco, October, 1991.

<li>Alessi, N.:  An Open Clinical Trial of Fluoxetine in Childhood Major Depressive Disorder.  American Academy of Child and Adolescent Psychiatry, San Francisco, October, 1991.

<li>Zubieta, J. and Alessi, N.:  Trazodone in the Treatment of Childhood Disorders.  American Academy of Child and Adolescent Psychiatry, San Francisco, October, 1991.
</ol>

