<HTML>
<HEAD>
<TITLE>Background on N. Alessi</TITLE>
</HEAD><BODY BGCOLOR="EEEEEE">
<B> <IMG hspace=3 SRC= "/web/images/dot_clear.gif"><A HREF="/">Home</A> | <A HREF="./">Up</A> | <A HREF="/web/tools/">Tools</A> | <A HREF="/web/help/">Help</A> | <A HREF="/web/scripts/comment.acgi">Send a comment</A></B>
<HR>
<H3>EDUCATION</H3>

	Professional:	Emory University Medical School, Atlanta, Georgia, 1972-76, M.D.<br>

<H3>POSTGRADUATE TRAINING</H3>

	1976-1977	Psychiatric Internship, University of Michigan Hospital, Ann Arbor, Michigan<br>

	1977-1980	Resident in Psychiatry, University of Michigan Hospital, Ann Arbor, Michigan<br>

	1978-1981	Fellow in Child and Adolescent Psychiatry, University of Michigan, Ann Arbor, Michigan<br>

	1981-1983	Research Fellow in Child Psychiatry, Mental Health Research Institute, University of Michigan, Ann Arbor, Michigan<br>

<H3>ACADEMIC APPOINTMENTS</H3>

	1983-1989	Assistant Professor of Psychiatry, School of Medicine, University of Michigan<br>

	1989-present	Associate Professor of Psychiatry, School of Medicine, University of Michigan<P>

<H3>CONSULTING POSITIONS</H3>

	1975-1976	Admitting Physician, Peach Tree-Parkwood Psychiatric Hospital, Atlanta, Georgia<BR>

	1978-1980	Consulting Psychiatrist, Octagon House, Methadone Maintenance Clinic, Ann Arbor, Michigan<BR>

	1979-1980	Medical Director, Octagon House, Methadone Maintenance Clinic, Ann Arbor, Michigan<BR>

	1981-1982	Research Consultant, Task Force on the Mentally Ill Adolescent Offender, State of Michigan<BR>

	1979-1984	Consulting Psychiatrist, Maxey Boys' Training School, Green Oaks Center, Whitmore Lake, Michigan<BR>

	1984-1986	Consulting Psychiatrist, Monroe County, Adolescent and Child Day Treatment Program, Monroe, Michigan<BR>

	1987-1989	Consulting Psychiatrist, Veterans Hospital, Ann Arbor, Michigan<BR>

	1987-1989	Research Consultant, Maxey Boys' Training School (Hawthorn Center) Whitmore Lake, Michigan<BR>

<H3>Other Relevant Information</H3>

	1983-present	Attending Physician, Child Inpatient Service, Department of Psychiatry, University of Michigan Medical Center<BR>

	1986-1990	Program Director, Child Psychiatry, Diagnostic and Research Unit, Child and Adolescent Psychiatric Hospital, Department of Psychiatry, University of Michigan<BR>

	1986-1989	Director, Child Affective Disorders Program, Child and Adolescent Psychiatric Hospital, Department of Psychiatry, University of Michigan<BR>

