<HEAD>
<TITLE>October 13, 1995 Announcements</TITLE>
</HEAD><BODY BGCOLOR="#EEFFFF">
<B><A HREF="/">Home</A> | <A HREF="./">Up</A> | <A HREF="/web/tools/">Tools</A> | <A HREF="/web/help/">Help</A> | <A HREF="/web/scripts/comment.acgi">Send a comment</A></B>
<HR>

<h1><IMG SRC="/web/images/pstaricn.gif" ALT="PsychStar Logo" ALIGN=RIGHT>Announcements (10/13/95):
</h1>

<ul>
<li> There is a new layout of the AACAP homepage, thanks to the efforts of a new team member, Emmanuelle Stephan.

<li> The PsychStar team will be presenting at the <A HREF="/web/aacap/meeting/">annual meeting of the American Academy of Child and Adolescent Psychiatry</A>, October 17-22.  We will be demonstrating the Web and the Website at an exhibition booth as well as making live updates to the website with pictures of the annual meeting (we hope).  Watch for a link from the AACAP homepage.

<li> The <A HREF="/web/aacap/meeting/program.pdf">annual meeting program</A> is available in Adobe Acrobat format.  This allows you to see it in the original format, but you need to download and install the Acrobat viewer.

<li> The University of Michigan Psychiatry Consultation-Liaison seminar schedule is also available for UM visitors.  
<a href="http://www.psych.med.umich.edu/web/UMpsych/announce/seminar.htm">
http://www.psych.med.umich.edu/web/UMpsych/announce/seminar.htm</a>

<li> We are now the new home for the Psychiatric Society for Informatics.  This organization is current being formed under the guidance of a steering committee lead by Marvin Miller.  We are requesting input from potential members for our proposed draft of bylaws.  If you are a psychiatrist interested in joining, please send your comments.
<A HREF="/web/psi/">http://www.psych.med.umich.edu/web/psi/</A>
</ul>
<H3>We are happy to add new links to:</H3><br>
<ul>
<li>Internet Mental Health: an extensive free encyclopedia of mental health information. <br>
<a href="http://www.mentalhealth.com/">
http://www.mentalhealth.com/</a>

<li>ICD-10 Chapter V (F)<br>
<a href="http://www.informatik.fh-luebeck.de/icd/welcome.html">http://www.informatik.fh-luebeck.de/icd/welcome.html</a>

<li>LewyNet: a site on dementias associated with Lewy bodies<br>
<a href="http://www.ccc.nottingham.ac.uk/~mpzjlowe/lewy/lewyhome.html">
http://www.ccc.nottingham.ac.uk/~mpzjlowe/lewy/lewyhome.html</a>

<li>GlobalPsych: a confederation of co-operating individuals and organizations designed to promote cordial and wide ranging debate and investigation of issues in health, behavior, cognition and education, from a broad
multi-disciplinary perspective. <br>
<a href="http://www.shef.ac.uk/uni/projects/gpp/">
http://www.shef.ac.uk/uni/projects/gpp/</a>
</ul>

<h3>This just in...</h3>
<ul>
<li> Our site had 73069 hits during the month of September!
</ul>
