<IMG SRC="/web/images/pstaricn.gif" align="left" vspace=5><H1>Psychiatric and Psychological Institutions</H1><BR CLEAR=ALL>
<HR>
<H2><A NAME="societies">Societies</A></H2>
<UL>
<LI><A HREF="http://apa.org/">American Psychiatric Association</A>
<LI>the <A HREF="/web/psi/">Psychiatric Society for Informatics</A>
<LI>the homepage of the <A HREF="/web/aacap/"><FONT size=+1><B>American Academy of Child and Adolescent Psychiatry</B></FONT></A>: contains information about the AACAP as well as their <A HREF="/web/aacap/factsFam/">Facts for Families</A> series of pamphlets.
<LI>Milton's <A HREF="/web/intpsych/"><FONT size=+1><B>InterPsych</B></FONT></A> page: a description of the Interpsych organization and some of the services they provide, including email and IRC discussion forums
<LI><A HREF="http://www.sob.org/"> Society of Biological Psychiatry</A>
<LI><A HREF="http://www.shef.ac.uk/uni/projects/gpp/ ">GlobalPsych</A>: a confederation of co-operating individuals and organizations designed to promote cordial and wide ranging debate and investigation of issues in health, behavior, cognition and education, from a broad multi-disciplinary perspective. 
<LI>APsa: <A HREF="http://apsa.org/">The American Psychoanalytic Association</A>
<LI>the homepage of the <A HREF="http://www.lafayette.edu/allanr/scip.html">Society for Computers in Psychology</A>: a non-profit organization of researchers interested in applications of computers in psychology
<LI>The <A HREF="http://psych.hanover.edu/APS/">American Psychological Society</A>
<LI>PsychNET: the home of the <A HREF="http://www.apa.org/">American Psychological Association</A>
<LI>the Abraham A. Brill Library's <A HREF="http://www.interport.net/nypsan/">Freudnet</A>: contains information about the library and psychoanalysis
<LI><A HREF="http://www.umdnj.edu/~pulierml/AAP.home.html">Administrators in Academic Psychiatry</A>, a professional organization for the
education and networking of administrators of academic departments of
psychiatry
<LI>Los Angeles Institute and 
Society for Psychoanalytic Studies(LAISPS)<A HREF=" http://home.earthlink.net/~laisps/">LAISPS</A>
</A>

</UL>

