<H1>UM Psychiatry Consultation-Liaison Seminar Series</H1><P>
<B>From: David Knesper, M.D. Director, Hospital Consultation Services<P></B>
<P>
<IMG SRC="/web/images/knesperl.gif" ALIGN="left" HSPACE=10 VSPACE=5>
<Font size=+1>

This seminar series has been developed in response to the directions being taken by the "new" psychiatry and in response to residents requests for a  more systematic coverage of consultation psychiatry. 

