<TITLE>Medical Library Informatics</TITLE>
</HEAD><BODY BGCOLOR="EEEEEE">
<B> <IMG hspace=3 SRC= "/web/images/dot_clear.gif"><A HREF="/">Home</A> | <A HREF="./">Up</A> | <A HREF="/web/tools/">Tools</A> | <A HREF="/web/help/">Help</A> | <A HREF="/web/scripts/comment.acgi">Send a comment</A></B>
<HR>
<H2>Medical Library Informatics</H2>
By Tony Aguirre
<P>

This presentation will deal with the role of libraries in Medical Informatics.  The role of the NLM in the development of medical libraries and medical informatics through its programs and  service, and as an example of these services, a brief!! tutorial  on the Unified Medical Language System.
<HR>
