<HR>
<H2>Internet Information Resources</H2>

by Dr. Milton Huang<P>
I will cover:
<UL>
<LI>What the Internet is; specifically, discussing Internet Protocols and Protocol Structure.
<LI>What informatiom resources are available relevant to Medicine, illustrating with a live demonstration.
<LI>Future trends on Internet use, both in terms of technology and how people will relate to such information resources.
</UL>
<HR>
