<H2>Towards New Knowledge Work Environments: <BR>
Digital Libraries and Collaboratories
</H2>
By Dan Atkins
<P>
I will describe :
<UL>
<LI>emerging work in human-centered system design to  support
team-based, distributed  intellectual work. 
<LI> examples from several experimental projects underway: the Upper Atmospheric Research Collaboratory and the UM Digital Library Project.

</UL>

