<H2>Glenn Hiller MS</H2>

I'm an Associate Director of MCIT responsible for Administrative Systems.
This includes the MCIT units of Medical School Information Systems,
Hospital Financial Systems, and Hospital Administratives Services.  I am
also responsible
for the Data Warehouse Project.  I received an MS in Computer &
Communication Sciences from the University of Michigan in 1971 and have
worked for the University since 1973.

