<TITLE>Community Health Networks</TITLE>
</HEAD><BODY BGCOLOR="EEEEEE">
<B> <IMG hspace=3 SRC= "/web/images/dot_clear.gif"><A HREF="/">Home</A> | <A HREF="./">Up</A> | <A HREF="/web/tools/">Tools</A> | <A HREF="/web/help/">Help</A> | <A HREF="/web/scripts/comment.acgi">Send a comment</A></B>
<HR>
<H2>Community Mental Health Networks</H2>
By Jocelyn DeWitt
<P>
  This lecture will povide an overview of community health information 
networks, including their benefits and the various approaches taken toward 
the implementation of a CHIN.  A brief description of the UMMC CHIN project 
and next steps will also be provided.
<HR>  
