<H2>Managing a Laboratory Information System:  Observations by a Bit 
Player</H2>
by Bruce Friedman
<P>

A discussion of how the management of an ancillary hospital system 
(the laboratory information system) has changed over the last decade 
with special emphasis on hospital-vendor relationships.

