<TITLE>Medical Records</TITLE>
</HEAD><BODY BGCOLOR="EEEEEE">
<B> <IMG hspace=3 SRC= "/web/images/dot_clear.gif"><A HREF="/">Home</A> | <A HREF="./">Up</A> | <A HREF="/web/tools/">Tools</A> | <A HREF="/web/help/">Help</A> | <A HREF="/web/scripts/comment.acgi">Send a comment</A></B>

<HR>

<H2>Medical Records and Patient Privacy in the traditional 
environment</H2>
by Ed Goldman and Sean Auton <P> 


 This will be a review of current State and Federal 
guidelines concerning Med Record policies and procedures, including 
research work and patient privacy. 
<P>
 Since there is a lot of material to 
cover, we'd like to reserve about a quarter of the time at the end to 
answer questions specific to the group.





