<TITLE>Fredrick M Wolf</TITLE>
</HEAD><BODY BGCOLOR="EEEEEE">

<B> <IMG hspace=3 SRC= "/web/images/dot_clear.gif"><A HREF="/">Home</A> | <A HREF="./">Up</A> | <A HREF="/web/tools/">Tools</A> | <A HREF="/web/help/">Help</A> | <A HREF="/web/scripts/comment.acgi">Send a comment</A></B>
<HR>
<H2>Decision Support System</H2>
<P>


 by Fredrick M Wolf <P>

 These are the software applications that help physicians decide on diagnosis and treatment.  Demonstrations will show the workings of IILAD (diagnosis support) and The Cochrane Database of Systematic Reviews  (CDSR) - a treatment support tool that attempts to summarize meta-analyses of all controlled randomized trials. <P>




