<B> <IMG hspace=3 SRC= "/web/images/dot_clear.gif"><A HREF="/">Home</A> | <A HREF="./">Up</A> | <A HREF="/web/tools/">Tools</A> | <A HREF="/web/help/">Help</A> | <A HREF="/web/scripts/comment.acgi">Send a comment</A></B>
<HR>
<H2>Fredric M. Wolf Ph.D</H2>
<P>

Fredric M. Wolf, Ph.D. is Professor of Postgraduate Medicine and Health
Professions Education and Director of the Learning Resource Center and
Laboratory for Computing, Cognition, & Clinical Skills at the University of
Michigan Medical School.  
<P>
<H3>Selected Recent Publications Include:</H3><BR>
<UL>
<LI>Fitzgerald JT, Wolf FM, Davis WK, et al.  A preliminary study of the impact
of case specificity on computer-based assessment of medical student clinical
performance.  Eval Health Prof 1994; 17: 307-321.<BR>
<P>
<LI>Grum C, Miller JG, Wolf FM.  Incorporation of computer-based primary care
diagnostic problem solving in an Internal Medicine clerkship.  Academic
Medicine 1994; 69: 429-430.<BR><P>

<LI>Hickey T, Robins LS, Wagner MB, Harik W, Wolf FM.  Physical activity training
for functional mobility in older persons.  J Applied Gerontology 1995; 14:
357-371.<BR>
<P>
<LI>Miller JG, Wolf, FM.  Strategies for integrating computer-based activities
into your educational environment:  A practical guide.  Journal of the
American Medical Informatics Association 1996; in press.<BR>
<P>
<LI>Miller, JG, Chapman CM, Bruenger JA, Judge RD, Perrin SR, Wolf FM.  CARDIAX:
Computer-aided review of diagnosis involving auscultation, x-ray (and EKG). 
Proc Annu Symp Comput Appl Med Care, 1993; 17: 956.<BR>
<P>
<LI>Sharpe PA, Hickey T, Wolf FM.  Adaptation of a general optimism scale for use
with older women.  Psychol Reports 1994;74: 931-937.<BR>
<P>
<LI>TenHaken JD, Woolliscroft JO, Smith JB, Wolf FM, Calhoun JG.  A longitudinal
examination of changes in medical students' attitudes toward the elderly. 
Teaching & Learning in Medicine 1995; 7:18-22.<BR>
<P>
<LI>Wolf FM, Miller JG, Bozynski ME, Schlesinger AE, Rosen DS, Weiner GM, Fliegel
JE.  Experience and case difficulty differences in the interpretation of
Pediatric radiographs.  Academic Medicine 1994; 69: S31-S33<BR>
<P>
<LI>Wolf FM, Sisson JC, Zweifler AZ.  A standardized patient program to evaluate
summarization skills in patient interviews.  Academic Medicine 1995; 70: 443<BR>

<LI>Wolf FM. Developing "Guidelines for meta-analyses evaluating diagnostic
tests". Ann Intern Med 1994; 817-818.<BR>

<LI>Wolf FM.  Problem-based learning and meta-analysis.  Academic Medicine
1993;68:542-545
<P>
</UL>
