http://www.psych.med.umich.edu:80/web/aacap/FactsFam/firearms.htm 141.214.71.83 19970121064050 text/html 5477
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
MIME-Version: 1.0
Server: WebSTAR/1.2.4 ID/39
Message-ID: <af09dc67.151845@141.214.71.83>
Date: Tuesday, 21-Jan-97 06:37:27 GMT
