<H4>"Know Where to Find Help for your Child" --Regional Organizations of Child and Adolescent Psychiatry</H4>  
These child and adolescent psychiatrists are the AACAP delegates to Regional Organizations of Child and Adolescent Psychiatry.  They can refer you to the appropriate professional or facility in your area.  For a referral in a state not covered by this list, call the AACAP Central Office at <B>1 (202) 966-7300</B>.<P>

