<HEAD><TITLE>Annual Meeting</TITLE>
</HEAD><BODY BGCOLOR="#EEFFFF">
<H2>PSI Annual Meeting</H2>
<P>
<B> Introduction: Data Management 
<P>
 By Norman Alessi M.D.</B>
<P>
At the core of all future successful psychiatric healthcare delivery  will be the development of integrated institutional information networks.  These will have to reflect the &quot; re-engineering&quot; of what we consider our work, and the development of well integrated data systems. 
<P>
 My presentation will review the necessary organizational changes we need to make in our human and information infrastructure to facilitate the deployment of such systems.
<P>

<P>
<A HREF="/web/psi/mtg/">Return to Annual Meeting</A>





