<H2>PSI Annual Meeting</H2>
<P>
<B>Business Process Reengineering
<P>
By Sheila Marcus M.D.</B>
<BR>
Lecturer. Dept. of Psychiatry<BR>
University of Michigan Medical School
<P>
Dr. Marcus is currently working at the University of Michigan Department of 
Psychiatry in the Managed Care Program. Dr. Marcus has been involved with the integration of managed care principles into the Department, integrating those
principles wih its academic mission.
<P>
Providing quality care for adults and children in a managed care culture and assisting the department in the transition from a Fee for Service to Managed
Care environment has been a recent focus of her work.
