<H2>PSI Annual Meeting</H2>
<P>
<B>By Steven E Hyler M.D.</B><P>

Clinical Databases for use in Psychiatry<P>
This presentation covers the basics of databases including: definition, 
parts, viewing data, layouts, types of databases, and specialized 
databases.
<P> 
There will be a brief demonstration of several commercially 
available database programs that will be of interest to psychiatrists.


<P>
