Adolescent Psychiatry Website in the Department of Psychiatry at the
University of Michigan Medical Center. 1996.</P>

<P>Abstracts</P>

<P>Alessi, N.E. and Quinlan, P.: Biochemical Studies of Postnatal
Development of Proopiomelanocortin-related Peptides in the Rat
Medulla Oblongata. Winter Neuropeptide Conference, Denver, Colorado,
January, 1985.</P>

<P>Quinlan, P.E.: The Neuroendocrine Effects of Interleukin-2
Treatment in Patients with Metastatic Carcinoma. The 5th Annual
Conference on Scientific Research in Osteopathic Medicine, East
Lansing, Michigan, October 1987.</P>

