<HR>
<IMG SRC="/web/images/pstaricn.gif" align="left"><H1>Anxiety Disorders</H1>
<UL>
<LI>NIMH <A HREF="gopher://gopher.gsa.gov:70/00/staff/pa/cic/health/panic">patient information pamphlet on Panic Disorder</A>
<LI>The NIH consensus statement on the <A HREF="http://text.nlm.nih.gov/nih/cdc/www/85txt.html" NAME="">Treatment of Panic Disorder</A>
<LI>The <A HREF="http://mtech.csd.uwm.edu/~fairlite/ocd.html">OCD homepage</A> maintained by <A HREF="http://mtech.csd.uwm.edu/~fairlite/ocd/about.html">Mark and Kelly Luljak</A>: includes several abstracts and articles on OCD, antidepressants, and patient resources
<LI><A HREF="http://gladstone.uoregon.edu/~dvb/trauma.htm">David Baldwin's Trauma Info Pages</A>: covers multiple aspects of Trauma and PTSD
<LI>The <A HREF="http://www.long-beach.va.gov/ptsd/stress.html">Traumatic Stress Home Page</A> maintained by the Carl T. Hayden VAMC in Phoenix Arizona.
<LI><A HREF="gopher://gopher.etext.org:70/00/Politics/NY.Transfer/vnam/ptsd_1.txt.gz" NAME="">The Etiology Of Combat-Related Post-Traumatic Stress Disorders</A>, by Jim Goodwin, Psy.D. from <I>Nam Vet News</I>
<LI><A HREF="http://www.cc.gatech.edu/gvu/virtual/Phobia/Phobia.html">Georgia Tech Virtual Reality Exposure Therapy</A>
</UL>

